<li><a href="Karl_Popper" title="Karl Popper">Popper, K.</a>, "On the Use and Misuse of Imaginary Experiments, Especially in Quantum Theory", pp.&#160;442–456, in Popper, K., <i>The Logic of Scientific Discovery</i>, Harper Torchbooks, (New York), 1968.</li>
